        "id": 1174099
      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-02-27T16:37:05Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "System without a functioning real-time clock keeping time while the power is off? I think that this can validly be 0 too. The real error condition would be if you didn’t find a btime at all.",
      "revId": "20e19b2def723d5c2a68e6f4aaf09a462947f2cc",
