      },
      "lineNbr": 129,
      "author": {
        "id": 1174099
      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-02-27T16:37:05Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "This is a good informative comment, but I don’t think that it should be a TODO. I don’t think we’ll ever care to support pre-2.6 kernels.",
      "revId": "20e19b2def723d5c2a68e6f4aaf09a462947f2cc",
