      },
      "lineNbr": 159,
      "author": {
        "id": 1172779
      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-02-27T17:28:07Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The only file I ran into this problem with was /proc/1/exe. (Some others are protected as well, but I don\u0027t need them yet.) This was just to figure out whether the process was 64-bit.",
      "parentUuid": "ad43f9b9_c4e8d8e4",
      "revId": "20e19b2def723d5c2a68e6f4aaf09a462947f2cc",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
